extends layout

block content
  nav(class='navbar navbar-light bg-trans fixed-top p-5')
    a(class='navbar-brand' href='#')
      img(src='/images/pizza_icon.png' width='30' height='30' class='d-inline-block align-top' alt='Pizza icon')
      span(class='lobster') #{title}
    ul(class='navbar-nav')
      li(class='nav-item')
  div(class='background-image section col-lg-12')
    div(class='container')
      div(class='row h-100')
        div(class='col-sm-12 my-auto')
          h1(class='title lobster')= title
          p(class='presentation-text') #{title} es un sitio te proporciona las herramientas necesarias para el desarrollo ágil, basado en la metodología Scrum.
          button(type='submit' class='m-1 text-center btn btn-outline-success active' data-toggle='modal' data-target='#signup') Registrarse
          button(type='submit' class='m-1 text-center btn btn-outline-success' data-toggle='modal' data-target='#login') Iniciar sesión
          br
          a(href='#section2' class='arrow-down float-right')
            i(class='fas fa-5x fa-angle-down' data-toggle='tooltip' data-placement='top' title='¿Por qué SCRUM?')
  div(class='section' id='section2')
    div(class='container')
      div(class='row h-100')
        div(class='col-sm-12 my-auto')
          h2(class='title-h2 lobster text-center') ¿Por qué Scrum?
          p(class='presentation-text text-center') Scrum = reglas + espíritu + buenas prácticas
          br
          br
          div(class='row mt-5')
            div(class='col-md-3 text-center')
              i(class='peperoni-color fas fa-7x fa-stopwatch')
              br
              br
              p(class='presentation-text text-center') Fomenta la productividad y predicción de tiempos.
            div(class='col-md-3 text-center')
              i(class='peperoni-color fas fa-7x fa-dollar-sign')
              br
              br
              p(class='presentation-text text-center') Ayuda a estimar costos y riesgos en el proyecto.
            div(class='col-md-3 text-center')
              i(class='peperoni-color fas fa-7x fa-hands-helping')
              br
              br
              p(class='presentation-text text-center') Promueve motivación y compromiso por el equipo de desarrollo.
            div(class='col-md-3 text-center')
              i(class='peperoni-color fas fa-7x fa-building')
              br
              br
              p(class='presentation-text text-center') Promueve autonomía y organización.
  div(id='login' class='modal fade bd-example-modal-lg' tabindex='-1' role='dialog' aria-labelledby='registrarse-modal' aria-hidden='true')
    div(class='modal-dialog modal-lg')
      div(class='modal-content')
        div(class='col-sm-12 my-auto form')
          h2(class='text-right') Iniciar sesión
           form
            div(class='form-group text-left')
              label(for='exampleInputEmail1') Correo electrónico
              input(type='email' class='form-control' id='exampleInputEmail1' aria-describedby='emailHelp' placeholder='yumi_pizza@scrumizza.com')
            div(class='form-group')
              label(for='exampleInputPassword1') Contraseña
              input(type='password' class='form-control' id='exampleInputPassword1' placeholder='Contraseña')
            div(class='form-group form-check')
              input(type='checkbox' class='form-check-input' id='exampleCheck1')
              label(class='form-check-label' for='exampleCheck1') Recordar contraseña
            button(type='submit' class='btn btn-outline-success') Iniciar sesión
  div(id='signup' class='modal fade bd-example-modal-lg' tabindex='-1' role='dialog' aria-labelledby='registrarse-modal' aria-hidden='true')
    div(class='modal-dialog modal-lg')
      div(class='modal-content')
        div(class='col-sm-12 my-auto form')
          h2(class='text-right') Iniciar sesión
           form
            div(class='form-group text-left')
              label(for='exampleInputEmail1') Correo electrónico
              input(type='email' class='form-control' id='exampleInputEmail1' aria-describedby='emailHelp' placeholder='yumi_pizza@scrumizza.com')
            div(class='form-group')
              label(for='exampleInputPassword1') Contraseña
              input(type='password' class='form-control' id='exampleInputPassword1' placeholder='Contraseña')
            div(class='form-group form-check')
              input(type='checkbox' class='form-check-input' id='exampleCheck1')
              label(class='form-check-label' for='exampleCheck1') Recordar contraseña
            button(type='submit' class='btn btn-outline-success') Iniciar sesión
            
            